COI neighbor-joining tree of available taxa of New World 
<taxonomicName box="[800,903,1654,1676]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="138" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Acontiinae">Acontiinae</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph blockId="15.[140,1108,167,616]" pageId="15" pageNumber="152">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[185,338,554,580]" pageId="15" pageNumber="152">
<emphasis box="[185,246,554,580]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="152" reason="1">Food</emphasis>
plants.
</emphasis>
Species have been reared from plant species in the families 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="15" pageNumber="152" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Malvaceae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[226,373,589,615]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Sterculiaceae" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="15" pageNumber="152" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Sterculiaceae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[384,504,589,615]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="15" pageNumber="152" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Asteraceae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="de Jussieu" authorityYear="1789" box="[516,697,589,615]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="15" pageNumber="152" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Convolvulaceae</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName box="[758,850,590,616]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="15" pageNumber="152" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Poaceae</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
